-- Formula One Driver Kubica Has Multiple Fractures After Crashing in Rally
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2011-02-06T14:15:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-06/formula-one-driver-kubica-has-multiple-fractures-after-crashing-in-rally.html
Lotus Renault Formula One driver  Robert Kubica  suffered multiple fractures to his right arm, leg
and hand in a “high speed” accident in a rally in  Italy  this
morning, the team said in an e-mailed statement.  He’s currently having surgery, the team added.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  